# VitalFlow Blood Donation Website

Welcome to our Blood Donation Website, a platform dedicated to connecting blood donors with receivers in need. This website facilitates easy communication between donors and receivers while ensuring the privacy and security of user data.

## Overview

Our Blood Donation Website aims to simplify the process of finding and donating blood. Users can register as donors or receivers, post blood requests, and communicate securely through the platform. Admins have access to a dashboard where they can monitor statistics and validate genuine donors.

## Features

- **User Registration**: Donors and receivers can register on the platform.
- **Post Blood Requests**: Receivers can post requests for specific blood types.
- **Secure Communication**: Users can chat with each other, ensuring real-time communication while keeping their credentials hidden.
- **Admin Dashboard**: Admins can view detailed statistics, manage users, and validate genuine donors.
- **Data Privacy**: User credentials are hidden to maintain privacy and security.
- **Searching and Filtering**: Users can look for donors by filtering blood griup, district, date of requirement and eligibility. 
- **Educational Contents**: Website provides educational contents related to blood donation to spread awareness. 

## Technology Stack

- **Front-end**: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Tailwind CSS
- **Back-end**: PHP
- **Database**: MySQL
- **Real-time Communication**: AJAX

